2) The selected row is deleted successful

Test case 2. Saving manually entered data on the edit page by clicking "Обновить" button

Pre-conditions:
1) Go to URL: http://v1.qalight.com.ua;
2) Log in (login-student,password-909090)
3) Make a record Фамилия:Иванов, Имя:Иван, Отчество:Иванович, Телефон: (495)1111-11-12

Steps to reproduce:
1) Click "Справочная система">"Сотрудники" links
2) Click record made and follow to the edit page
3) Edit Фамилия column, enter "Пузанов"and click"Обновить" button


*Expected result:*
# A list of employees is opened
# User is redirected to the edit page and may edit all manually entering data
# Edited data is saved

